name: Document_cloneTest
description: Unit tests for the clone functionality of the Document class.

description: Unit tests for the shallowClone method of the Document class.

test_cases.name: testShallowClone
test_cases.description: Tests the shallowClone method of the Document class to ensure that the clone has the same properties but different references for certain attributes.

test_cases.description: Tests the outputSettings functionality with a valid OutputSettings object.
